instructions: Access your device s main drive and look for system . Select it, and then tap on bin . From there, delete busybox and su . By the way, these might not be there. If that is the case, move on to the next step. Go back to the system folder and select xbin . If the files are there, go ahead and delete both busybox and su . Go back to the system folder and select app . Delete superuser,apk . Restart the device and it will all be done.
